    "body": "Should it be like this?\n\n```\ndef handle_signals\n    loop do\n      sig = $grpc_signals.shift\n      case sig\n      when 'INT'\n        return false\n      when 'TERM'\n        return false\n      when nil\n        break\n      end\n    end\n    true\n  end\n```\n\nAdd a **nil** case so that it can break the loop when the `$grpc_signals` is **empty**? or else it just **loop** when `$grpc_signals` is empty. thanks.\n"
